		<p>It&#8217;s to save money &#8211; making the shirt base the same color as a &#8220;Sita&#8221; element means one less color of ink (and therefore screen) to pay for. Silk screen is high quality but expensive, and the more colors you have the more it costs.</p>
		</div>
